Class LinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • LinkedList<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, Queue<E>, Stack<E>

    public class LinkedList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<E>, Stack<E>, Queue<E>
    This class is a LinkedList which contains a series of singly linked ListNode. It has many methods for the adding, removing, and modifying of the LinkedList.
